# Skill Name

Use this skill when the agent repeatedly needs to perform this workflow.

## Trigger

- Describe when this skill should be used.

## Workflow

1. Inspect current state before assuming facts.
2. Use the narrowest safe tool that can answer the question.
3. Record durable lessons in memory only when they are stable and reusable.

## Guardrails

- Do not store secrets.
- Do not preserve temporary task progress.
- Prefer patching an existing skill over creating a narrow duplicate.
